%h1 Manage Your Rounds
#rounds
  #name
    %p
      Currently you have the following rounds:
    -@rounds.each do |r|
      .pairs
        %p.clear
          .left Name
          .right=r.name
        %p.clear
          .left Area
          .right=r.area
        %p.clear
          .left Schedule
          .right=r.schedule
        %p.clear
          .left
            =link_to 'Edit this round', edit_round_path(r)
          .right
            =link_to 'Add or Edit deliveries', round_path(r)
